code: @Override public void join(Tuple2<K, I1> value1, Tuple2<K, I2> value2, Collector<OUT> collector) throws Exception {     wrappedFunction.join(unwrap(value1), unwrap(value2), collector). }
@SuppressWarnings("unchecked") private <V> V unwrap(Tuple2<K, V> t) {     return t == null ? null : (V) (t.getField(1)). }
